transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Sir, main keh raha hoon aapse pooch ke toh maine category ki thi, abhi aapne phir dobara se no de diya. Main aapse bol ke toh bola hai na sir usko satisfy mark kijiye.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Jo aapne bola woh change kar diya uske baad bhi aap no de rahe hain sir.
Executive: Nahi toh no toh yeh abhi bande ko bolta hoon usne kya kiya hoga. 
Customer: Puch ke tabhi toh kiya na sir waha pe ek ek bande ki performance pe sir.
Executive: Nahi toh no.
Customer: Chalo main abhi karwata hoon usko wapis.
Executive: Ji.
